comments: Ball (NOP) is moving alongside MIddleton's (MIL) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) is bracing for the contact from Adams (NOP) when he releases away.
Middleton (MIL) places his hand momentarily on Adams' (NOP) side before immediately removing his hand.
Adams (NOP) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.

Lopez (MIL) collapses his left arm against his body upon contact and jumps vertically with his right arm raised as he contests Williamson's (NOP) shot attempt at the rim. Lopez reaches forward with his right arm but avoids making arm contact with Williamson.
WIlliamson (NOP) releases his shot attempt before his foot returns to the floor.
Ball (NOP) is moving alongside Antetokounmpo's (MIL) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive.
Ball (NOP) brushes Antetokounmpo's (MIL) side as he defends the driving shot attempt, and contact is marginal.
Middleton (MIL) legally contests Ingram's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
WIlliamson (NOP) and Antetokounmpo (MIL) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) is already in Ball's (NOP) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Williamson (NOP) and DiVIncenzo (MIL) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Ball (NOP) legally contests Middleton's (MIL) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Ingram (NOP) and Portis (MIL) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes contact with Adams' (NOP) arm as he gets his hand on the rebound and it affects his ability to control the ball.
Ball (NOP) commits a take foul on Middleton (MIL).
Antetokounmpo (MIL) inbounds the ball within five seconds.
Ball (NOP) makes clean contact with the ball as he defends Middleton (MIL) on the perimeter.
WIlliamson (NOP) cleanly deflects the ball away from Middleton (MIL).
Williamson's (NOP) foot is out of bounds when he makes contact with the ball.
Ingram (NOP) splits his feet on the perimeter.
Ingram (NOP) initiates contact with DiVincenzo (MIL), who has established a legal guarding position in his path.
Ingram (NOP) commits a take foul on Antetokounmpo (MIL).
